        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/42800848/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/42800848/" class="">第4页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/rollingge/" class=" " title="如林">如林</a>
                (林无静树 川无停流)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="42800848">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">认为他们所施展的强暴狡诈，背信弃义种种卑劣手段，只要有利于实现目标，都是可取的。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-04-02 07:27</span>
                  
                </p>
